    "(uplink transmission) (8)Algorithm 1 Two-phase Matching-based Association (TMA)1: Initialization: Obtain the channel gain matrix H between all mobile devices and edge servers.",
    "2: Phase 1: Channel Gain-based Pre-evaluation 3: for all m ∈ M do 4: Select the edge server e with the highest gain H m,e. 5: Set X m,e ← 1.",
    "6: end for 7: Phase 2: Iterative Swap-based Optimization 8: while swap pair exists do 9:for all (m, e), (m ′, e ′) with X m,e = X m ′,e ′ = 1 do Set X m,e ′ ← 1 and X m ′,e ← 1.",
    "13:Reset X m,e ← 0, X m ′,e ′ ← 0.14: end if 15:end for 16: end while Then, our optimization objective I can be formulated as min X,Y,Z i∈M j∈Ex ij D MD i + D ES ij + λ D MD i - d i R i2 2 (P 1)+ w i∈M E CP i + E CM i B i s.t.",
    "(3), ( 4), (7).where λ is a penalty for latency synchronization, and w is a unit conversion factor normalizing energy efficiency."
